# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

<!-- ## [Unreleased] -->
## [1.2.1] - 2022-02-17
### Fixed
- The `prune` command runs in an endless loop without the "--force" option

## [1.2.0] - 2022-02-17
### Added
- Added prettier to format code base
### Changed
- Increased the performance of the prune command
- Renamed `prune --stats` output "Total size" to "Estimated size"
- Updated some dependencies to their latest minor version
### Removed
- Removed folder count from `prune --stats`


## [1.1.0] - 2021-10-15
### Added
- Add additional patterns for new config files

### Changed
- prune command uses the default patterns when no ".modprunerrc" was found ([#2](https://github.com/y-kalka/mod-pruner/issues/2))

## [1.0.0] - 2021-09-10
### Added
- Add "prune" command which cleanes all node_modules folder under the current working directory
- Add "init" command to quickly create a config file with some default rules
